Hi,
We are going to have a crack at building the complex version of the Hub.
I am hoping there is a fusion 360 CAD file available for the cutout layout of the 6 sheets of 3/4" ply, 1 sheet of 1/2" ply and 2 sheets of 1/8" polycarb as shown on the drawings on pages 5-14 of the ReadMe_Complex_TE-22100_and_TE-22100-AM.pdf that is inside the Assembly1_Complex.zip file. Link to file

There appears to be a zip file full of solidwork files inside this main zip file. Unfortunately I have no idea how to use solidworks. Can someone that is building the complex model of the hub export these cutout layouts files into a STEP format and post them here for the Fusion 360 users.
Thanks again in advance.
Warren
